caption: #contest Hi! My Name is Maor and I'm 14 years old and you guys are my idols.. You guys have changed my life in so many positive ways. All I want to do is say Thank you in person. You guys taught me that's it's okay to be me. I love to sing and because of you guys I started putting myself out there.. I started to sing in public and not really care about what other people thought about me. Thank you guys for being you. You guys have put such a positive affect on me. Love you ?
